content.data:
SHE’S COMPLICATED
This is Agency Andys Displate collection-

Familiar Breeds.

1 SHE’S COMPLICATED
2 EYES
3 YOU CAN LOOK OVER BUT THAT'S IT
4 UPWARDLY
5 LOVE IS HARD

Andy Ulanoff has been trying to use art to tell familiar stories in an unfamiliar - even alienating way. Andy likes the way color and shape can make an image seem more approachable or alienating depending on color or subtle shifts of line.Andy likes the bold and often bad color combinations that wake you up a little. Andy often uses flat colors and a naive design to coney the message.

Andy’s art lives here on hello and on instagram.

https://www.instagram.com/agencyandy/
https://www.agencyandy.com
